TITLE: Defining Scalar Arguments using t.arg Method in Pothos
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define scalar arguments using the t.arg method in Pothos. It creates a string field with a string argument.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/website/content/docs/guide/args.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
