TITLE: Setting up GraphQL Server with Yoga
DESCRIPTION: Creating and configuring a GraphQL server using graphql-yoga with the Pothos schema.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/website/content/docs/guide/objects.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_4

