TITLE: Inferring Input and Object Types from Refs in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use $inferInput and $inferType properties on Pothos refs to extract TypeScript types from input types and Prisma objects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/website/content/docs/guide/inferring-types.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const MyInput = builder.inputType('MyInput', {
  fields: (t) => ({
    id: t.id({ required: true }),
    name: t.string({ required: true }),
  }),
});

// { id: string; name: string; }
type MyInputShape = typeof MyInput.$inferInput;

// infer the shape of the Prisma User model
const UserRef = builder.prismaObject('User', {});
type UserType = typeof UserRef.$inferType;
```

