TITLE: Customizing Relation Queries with Filtering and Ordering
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to customize relation fields with filtering, ordering, and pagination by specifying a query option that accepts GraphQL arguments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/plugin-drizzle/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
