TITLE: Selecting nested GraphQL fields with nestedSelection in Typescript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use `nestedSelection` to select fields from a nested GraphQL field, specifically within a `User` object to fetch `Post` previews. It showcases limiting the number of posts to load using `take` and using typeName to get selections for a specific object type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/website/content/docs/plugins/prisma/indirect-relations.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
