TITLE: Defining Drizzle Connection for Posts in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a drizzleConnection for fetching published posts. It specifies the ordering of posts based on their IDs in descending order.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/plugin-drizzle/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
builder.queryFields((t) => ({
  posts: t.drizzleConnection({
    type: 'posts',
    resolve: (query, root, args, ctx) =>
      db.query.posts.findMany(
        query({
          where: (post, { eq }) => eq(post.published, true),
          orderBy: (post) => ({ desc: post.id }),
        }),
      ),
  }),
}));
```

