TITLE: GraphQL Query for Handling Validation Errors
DESCRIPTION: Example query that demonstrates how to handle validation errors by including fragments for both the success case and the ZodError case to access field-level validation errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/deno/packages/plugin-errors/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query {
  validation(string: "a") {
    __typename
    ... on QueryValidationSuccess {
      data
    }
    ... on ZodError {
      fieldErrors {
        message
        path
      }
    }
  }
}
```

