TITLE: Validating Lists with Zod Plugin in Pothos
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to validate list arguments by applying validation to individual list items and the overall list properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/deno/packages/plugin-zod/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
builder.queryType({
  fields: (t) => ({
    list: t.boolean({
      nullable: true,
      args: {
        list: t.arg.stringList({
          validate: {
            items: {
              email: true,
            },
            maxLength: 3,
          },
        }),
      },
      resolve: () => true,
    }),
  }),
});
```

