DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to query a field that uses the Errors plugin, using fragments to handle both success and error cases in the response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/deno/packages/plugin-errors/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

