TITLE: Implementing Object Type for Loadable Object - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines an object type for the User loadable object, specifying the necessary fields. It represents an integration of loadable references with object types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hayes/pothos/blob/main/packages/deno/packages/plugin-dataloader/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
